    "description": "<p><p class=\"Body-Foundation\">People know who you are and what you’ve done, and they treat you differently because of it. When you leverage your notoriety to get what you want, you can <strong>mark a </strong><tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"stress\" nexus=\"daggerheart\"><strong>Stress</strong></tooltip> before you roll to gain a +10 bonus to the result. Your food and drinks are always free wherever you go, and everything else you buy is reduced in price by one <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"bag-gold\" nexus=\"daggerheart\">bag of gold</tooltip> (to a minimum of one <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"handful-gold\" nexus=\"daggerheart\">handful</tooltip>).        </p><p class=\"Body-Foundation\">This card doesn’t count against your <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"loadout-and-vault\" nexus=\"daggerheart\">loadout’s</tooltip> domain card maximum of 5 and can’t be placed in your vault.</p></p>",
